      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我刚才默认加了箭头标签，现在去掉。改成metric0到metric1的无标签实线连接，保持流向清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "metric0",
        "metric1"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "调整完成了。最终结构：左侧metric0（HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine）→ 右侧metric1（HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault），左右流向，小字体样式，无标签连接线。你确认一下是否符合要求？",
